			p I work at <a href="https://learnvest.com">LearnVest</a>, where I help to organize design systems across our User Interfaces, and build the software that breathes life into them. I also teach web-engineering courses at the <a href="http://nycda.com">New York Code &amp; Design Academy</a>. In both places, I'm lucky to be surrounded by awesome, passionate people.